  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best international schools in Bangalore with the IGCSE Board?",
  "response": "Bangalore, also known as Bengaluru, is home to several prestigious international schools offering the IGCSE (International General Certificate of Secondary Education) curriculum. Here are some of the best IGCSE schools in Bangalore:\n\n1. **Canadian International School (CIS)**\n   - **Location:** Yelahanka, Bangalore\n   - **Overview:** CIS is known for its strong academic program and comprehensive extracurricular activities. The school offers both IGCSE and IB (International Baccalaureate) programs.\n   - **Website:** [Canadian International School](https://www.cisb.org.in/)\n\n2. **Bangalore International School (BIS)**\n   - **Location:** Whitefield, Bangalore\n   - **Overview:** BIS is a well-regarded institution offering the IGCSE curriculum. The school is known for its emphasis on holistic education, including sports and arts.\n   - **Website:** [Bangalore International School](https://www.bangaloreinternationalschool.org/)\n\n3. **Indus International School**\n   - **Location:** Sarjapur, Bangalore\n   - **Overview:** Indus International School offers the IGCSE curriculum and is known for its state-of-the-art facilities and strong academic performance. The school also focuses on leadership and community service.\n   - **Website:** [Indus International School](https://www.indusschool.com/)\n\n4. **Stonehill International School**\n   - **Location:** Hebbal, Bangalore\n   - **Overview:** Stonehill is part of the prestigious network of Nord Anglia Education schools. It offers the IGCSE and IB programs and is known for its excellent faculty and facilities.\n   - **Website:** [Stonehill International School](https://www.stonehillinternational.com/)\n\n5. **Greenwood High International School**\n   - **Location:** Sarjapur Road, Bangalore\n   - **Overview:** Greenwood High offers the IGCSE curriculum and is known for its strong academic programs and extensive extracurricular activities. The school focuses on developing well-rounded students.\n   - **Website:** [Greenwood High International School](https://www.greenwoodhigh.edu.in/)\n\n6. **Inventure Academy**\n   - **Location:** Whitefield, Bangalore\n   - **Overview:** Inventure Academy is known for its innovative approach to education and offers the IGCSE curriculum. The school emphasizes critical thinking, creativity, and personal development.\n   - **Website:** [Inventure Academy](https://www.inventureacademy.com/)\n\nWhen choosing the best school for your child, consider factors such as location, fees, extracurricular offerings, and the specific needs and interests of your child. It\u2019s also a good idea to visit the schools, meet with the admissions teams, and get a feel for the campus environment.",
